spec_data.Name: perl-CGI-Application-Plugin-TT
spec_data.Description:
CGI::Application::Plugin::TT adds support for the popular Template Toolkit
engine to your CGI::Application modules by providing several helper methods
that allow you to process template files from within your runmodes.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 08:08:41 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Add Template Toolkit support to CGI::Application
